r.isA(variables.get(varName), \"org.assertj.core.api.AbstractSoftAssertions\"); this assertj doesn't seem to be needed as a compile dependency.", "url": "https://github.com/pmd/pmd/pull/2465#discussion_r422985793", "createdAt": "2020-05-11T11:54:14Z", "author": {"login": "KroArtem"}, "path": "pom.xml", "diffHunk": "@@ -664,8 +664,8 @@\n             </dependency>\n             <dependency>\n                 <groupId>org.mockito</groupId>\n-                <artifactId>mockito-all</artifactId>\n-                <version>1.10.19</version>\n+                <artifactId>mockito-core</artifactId>", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQyMTMwOTgwNA=="}, "originalCommit": {"oid": "3fba3f6217b827a7c51b9524c247f9c286731553"}, "originalPosition": 15}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQyMjk5OTk4NA==", "bodyText": "I've removed assertj from root pom as it's not used anywhere except pmd-java, also moved mockito, wiremock, system-rules under  and marked them with test scope", "url": "https://github.com/pmd/pmd/pull/2465#discussion_r422999984", "createdAt": "2020-05-11T12:22:16Z", "author": {"login": "KroArtem"}, "path": "pom.xml", "diffHunk": "@@ -664,8 +664,8 @@\n             </dependency>\n             <dependency>\n                 <groupId>org.mockito</groupId>\n-                <artifactId>mockito-all</artifactId>\n-                <version>1.10.19</version>\n+                <artifactId>mockito-core</artifactId>", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQyMTMwOTgwNA=="}, "originalCommit": {"oid": "3fba3f6217b827a7c51b9524c247f9c286731553"}, "originalPosition": 15}]}}, {"id": "MDIzOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3VGhyZWFkMjYyMjkzOTE4OnYy", "diffSide": "RIGHT", "path": "pom.xml", "isResolved": true, "comments": {"totalCount": 3, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyMC0wNS0wN1QwODoyMjoxNFrOGRzsKA==", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyMC0wNS0yMlQwOTozOTowMFrOGZRCpA==", "hasNextPage": 